            <title>[LU-10532] Need CentOS 6.9 kernel support in b2_7_fe</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10532</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Our production Lustre servers are running CentOS 6.8 and Lustre 2.7.3 FE.&lt;br/&gt;
